author: woman/female

author: wife
glottocode: Certainly a reflex of *biha (cf. Atoni); the lack of segmentation of the possessive -n has lead to erroneous associated with *binay

author: fog
glottocode: Also foho dubun 'fog (in the mountains)', literally, mountain steam/smoke

author: green
glottocode: Also means uncooked (eg. of meat, water), still soft (of cement); unripe; green (eg. of leaves)
